quran[19]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,181,"Soni ntendele uŵe kwa Achimitenga."
  37,182,"Soni lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope."
  43,70,"Jinjilani ku Mbepo, jenumanja ni achiŵammakwenu ŵakwe tim’be nkusengwasyidwa."
  43,71,"Tisikaŵeje silinkwasyungula mbale syagolodi kwisa soni migao (jagolodi), ni timukaŵe mwana mwalakwemo yatiyikalaluchileje mitima, ni kusengwasya meso, soni jenumanja mwalakwemo tinkaŵe ŵandamo."
  43,72,"Soni jalakweji ni Mbepo ajila jampedwile kujitawala ligongo lya ayila yamwaliji nkupanganya."
  44,55,"Takaŵilasyeje mwalakwemo ntundu uliose wa isogosi mwantunjelele."
  44,56,"Ngasaja kupasya chiwa mwalakwemo ikaŵeje chiwa chao chandanda (cha pa duniya), ni taakaagoose ku ilagasyo ya Moto Waukali."
  44,57,"Kwa ukoto wakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah), chisimu kwalakweko ni kupunda kwekulungwa nnope."
  46,34,"Sano lisiku lyatachionesyedwa ku Moto aŵala ŵaŵakufuulu (tachiwusyidwa kuti): “Ana ayi nganiyiŵa yakuona?” Ŵanganyao tachiti: “Elo (yakuona) tukwalumbila Ambuje ŵetu.” (Allah) tachiti: “Basi pasyani ilagasyo ligongo lya ayila yamwaliji nkuikana.”"
  46,35,"Basi pililani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) yaŵatite pakupilila Achimitenga ŵakulimbangana nnope (pa dini, mpela Nuhu, Ibrahima, Musa ni Isa), ni ngasimwatendela chitema ŵanganyao (achimakafilio kuti yapate ilagasyo mwachitemachitema). Lisiku lyatachiyiona (ilagasyo) yaakupedwa chilanga (chakwika kwakwe), tachiŵa nti chisawu ŵanganyao nganatama (pa duniya) ikaŵeje ndaŵi jimpepe ja muusi. (Aji Qur’an jiŵele) utenga wakulungusyidwa (mwakwanila), ana (nkwika ilagasyoyo) mpaka ajonasiche (ŵanepe) pangaŵaga ŵandu ŵakunyosya?"
  47,25,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaagalauchile ku migongo jao (ku ukafili) panyuma pakumanyukuka kukwao chongoko, shetani jwasalalichisye (itendo yao yangalumbana), soni (Allah) nijwapele ndaŵi jelewu."
  47,26,"Yalakweyo ni ligongo lyanti ŵanganyao (achinakunaku) ŵatite pakwasalila aŵala (achimakafili) ŵaŵaichimile ayila yaŵatulwisye Allah: “Chitunkunde ine mu ichindu (yenu, mpela yakum’benga Muhammadi ﷺ, ni kwagwisya ulesi ŵakusaka kuja kumenyana namwe ngondo).” Sano Allah ni akumanyilila asili syao."
  47,27,"Ana ichiŵa uli ndema jatachatyosyaga Achimalaika maumi gao pakuwa, achaputaga ngope syao ni migongo jao?"
  48,16,"Mwasalilani akusigalila munyuma mu ŵarabu ŵanchimisi (kuti): “Sampano tim’bilanjidwe wa (kumenyana nao) ŵandu ŵaakwete machili gakuputila ngondo mwaukali, tinkamenyane nao kapena takagambe kulipeleka. Basi naga nkunde, Allah tampe malipilo gambone, nambo naga n’galauche (kuleka kumenyana nao) yamwatite paagalauka kalakala, tannagasye ni ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope.”"
  48,17,"Pangali gambidwa kwa jwangalola, soni pangali gambidwa kwa jwannemale, nambo soni pangali gambidwa kwa jwakulwala (naga ngaakwaula kungondo). Soni jwatampikanile Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, takan’jinjisye ku Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima sulo chapasi pakwe. Sano jwatagalauche, nikuti tannagasye ni ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope."
  48,18,"Chisimu pamasile paŵasengwele Allah ŵakulupilila ndema jaŵataŵanaga namwe (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) chilanga pasi pachitela, basi ni jwamanyilile yayaliji m’mitima mwao, ni ŵatuluchisye kutulala, ni ŵalipile kuwugula kwakuŵandika (kwakuwugula nsinda wa Khaibara ni Maaka)."
  49,4,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakum’bilanga (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ n’di) kusyeto kwa yumba, ŵajinji ŵao ŵangali lunda."
  49,5,"Soni ingaŵe ŵanganyao ŵapilile kuti mpaka nkopoche kuja kukwao, ingaliji yambone kwa jamanjao. Sano Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope."
  49,6,"E junumanja ŵankulupilile! Naga juli jum’bichilile jwangakulupichika ni abali jilijose (ngasimunkulupilila), nambo n’jiwungunye (kaje), ntakwika mwamwalagasyisye ŵandu mwa ujinga, basi ni kusyuka kuŵa ŵakuligamba pa yampanganyisye."